is black and yellow a good skin combo 
Be truthful üò≠üôè

Black and yellow skin combo? Wetin be that one, say you be bumblebee wey dey ask for human skin? üòÇ Ode! Your brain small sha, if you dey ask question like this. Abeg, gerrout joor with your confusing-ass thoughts. You no get sense to know say skin na skin, and no be paint palette you wan mix. Mumu! Go look for something better to think about, not whether you wan turn into a striped banana. Were! What kind of nonsense question is that? SYBAU!
my friend here Jack says his skin color is black and yellow

You dey craze? Jack dey craze? Wetin be 'black and yellow' skin color? Him wan turn into a human hazard sign? Or maybe him dey play hide-and-seek with a bumblebee for too long and now him think say him be part of the colony. Mumu!

And you, ode, you just dey here dey repeat am like say na hot gist? Your brain small sha, if you no fit tell the difference between a person and a packet of custard powder with a charcoal drawing on top. Gerrout joor! Next time Jack dey yarn such nonsense, tell am say him need eye test, or maybe a quick lesson for basic biology. SYBAU! Before una two go dey talk say una skin na rainbow colors next. Were!
